wG"></div></div><div id="frameInner" class="sc-dfVpRl kHAEbh"><article class="sc-bJTOcE kBhvfa"><div class="sc-RcBXQ jhRVwp"><div id="topBanner"></div></div><div id="nativeBanner" class="sc-iSDuPN fZuffm"></div><div id="adSlotWallpaper" class="sc-iSDuPN fZuffm"></div><div class="sc-geAPOV jPpguZ"><div id="content-wrapper" class="sc-dPPMrM hWAzky"><nav class="sc-jqIZGH sc-jMMfwr iZMQnl"><a href="/news">News</a><a href="/news/long-reads">Long Reads</a></nav><h1 class="sc-cBrjTV fHdQtt">I swapped chores with my husband to learn why women do 12 more days of housework every year</h1><h2 class="sc-jUpvKA ckENlX">The chore gap between the genders is widening, so Sophie Morris changed roles with her husband to see how it would affect their lives</h2><div class="sc-kEmuub ddqkkO sc-cqPOvA kZTOq"><a href="/author/sophie-morris" class="sc-iuDHTM dTuOma"><amp-img src="/images-i.jpimedia.uk/imagefetch/https://inews.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Sophie-Morris.png?width=200&amp;crop=1:1,smart" height="60" width="60" layout="fixed" class="i-amphtml-layout-fixed i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" style="width:60px;height:60px;" i-amphtml-layout="fixed"></amp-img></a><div class="sc-yZwTr cEbkYV"><div class="sc-erNlkL bnMauT"><a href="/author/sophie-morris"><span>By</span> Sophie Morris</a></div><div class="sc-hwcHae jAOtXc">Wednesday, 11th March 2020, 4:26 pm</div><div class="sc-hwcHae jAOtXc">Updated <amp-timeago layout="fixed-height" height="20" datetime="2020-03-11T18:29:38.000Z" cutoff="86400" locale="en" class="i-amphtml-layout-fixed-height i-amphtml-layout-size-defined" style="height:20px;" i-amphtml-layout="fixed-height">Wednesday, 11th March 2020, 6:29 pm</amp-timeago></div></div><div class="sc-kgoBCf dscUnr"><amp-social-share type="email" width="33" height="33" data-position="in article - top" data-vars-event="gaEvent" data-vars-ec="social" data-vars-ea="email share" data-vars-aidclick="2447244" data-vars-titleclick="I swapped chores with my husband to learn why women do 12 m